channel.description:

Starting portqry.exe -n xxx.xxx.x.x -e 43594 -p BOTH ...
Querying target system called:
xxx.xxx.x.x
Attempting to resolve IP address to a name...
IP address resolved to family-c4yjj2w6.Belkin
querying...
TCP port 43594 (unknown service): NOT LISTENING
UDP port 43594 (unknown service): LISTENING or FILTERED portqry.exe -n xxx.xxx.x.x -e 43594 -p BOTH exits with return code 0x00000002.
Also my modem is connected to my xbox, idk if this changes anything but figured i would put it out there..
